1. to create segue from login button to login screen --> ctrl+drag the button into the loginViewController, don't forget to give the segue an identity 
2. to make password titik titik item, go to passwordTextField property, check the "secure text entry"
3. Mandatory for creating tableView :
    a. What cell to be displayed
    b. How many cells

4. to show keyboard in textField, we use
    textFieldDidBeginEditing : is when the textField is pressed, show the keyboard
    textFieldDidEndEditing : is when the textField is out of focus (we press outside the textField), close down the keyboard, but we have to trigger it (not automatically closed) , so we use
        let tapGesture = UITapGestureRecognizer(target: self, action:#selector(tableViewTapped))



